From efd3c21b2d38a6cfbc771adbf4bcb2fd6b40520e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Zach Clifford <zachclifford@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 30 May 2026 12:40:52 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Add event-driven debugger: m6809 hooks + PinmameDebug*
 API + CMakeLists

Adds the event-driven CPU debugger to libpinmame:
- m6809 dispatch-loop hooks: pinmame_dbg_check_pc / pinmame_dbg_check_mem
  (gated on LIBPINMAME so VPinMAME COM builds are unaffected)
- Full PinmameDebug* API: Attach/Detach, AddBreakpoint/Watchpoint,
  DebugWait (blocks emulation thread on condvar), Continue, Step
- CMakeLists_libpinmame.txt for cmake -S . builds
- Alias.cpp: upstream ROM alias additions (VPinMAME COM only)

diff --git a/CMakeLists_libpinmame.txt b/CMakeLists_libpinmame.txt
new file mode 100644
index 00000000..e060cc0e
--- /dev/null
+++ b/CMakeLists_libpinmame.txt
@@ -0,0 +1,775 @@
